name: One Way Path at Millen Road
aboutDescription: One Way Path Communities builds multi-residential housing in liveable communities in and around the Greater Toronto Hamilton Area. These projects present an opportunity for equity investors to earn high rates of return with limited risk. Interested equity and debt partners are invited to contact info@onewaypath.com for more information.

name: On-Nūm Meditation Centre
aboutDescription: The On-Nūm Meditation Center is operated by One Way Path in Lieberose, Germany. We provide insight meditation based on the four foundations of mindfulness in the Therevada Buddhist Tradition.
